Module opentdk.gui
Package org.opentdk.gui.chart

Class ChartMarker

java.lang.Object
org.opentdk.gui.chart.ChartMarker
public final class ChartMarker extends Object
This class gets used to store marker information for the chart creation. The ChartMarker.marker(..) methods simply create a new marker to use it for further operations. A marker can be every JavaFX Shape or a Pane with Shape children to display additional information in the chart that is not connected to the chart data.
Author:
FME (LK Test Solutions)
